HEADWORD: Saprophytic
<hw>Sap`ro*phyt"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Feeding or
growing upon decaying animal or vegetable matter; pertaining to a
saprophyte or the saprophytes.</def>⟦br⟧
